  "StockRole": "Brawler",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Telesilla is a Majesty Metals design built around the Binary Laser Cannon, which tells you the Magistracy was willing to experiment with technology that most Inner Sphere manufacturers had quietly set aside for good reason. The original model went into MAF service despite mixed field trials, which is the kind of decision that makes more sense when you understand how limited Periphery procurement options were during the Succession Wars. The 511 upgrade addressed most of the structural complaints and turned it into a machine that actually delivers on what the original was trying to be.",
